      <title>Timer</title>
      <link href="/2023/11/14/timer/"/>
      <url>/2023/11/14/timer/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>给首页加了个小小的正计时～</p><p>其实代码改动不大，只需要把计算倒计时公式的减数和被减数调换，并删去最后限制无限制倒计时的代码就好了。</p><p>以下是<code>timer.ejs</code>的完整内容↓</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;% if (theme.timer.on &amp;&amp; page.current === 1) &#123; %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;div class=&quot;timer&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;h3 class=&quot;timer-title&quot; style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;自&lt;b style=&quot;color: #f19ec2;&quot;&gt;&lt;%= theme.timer.title %&gt;&lt;/b&gt;起，我们已经认识了……&lt;/h3&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;div class=&quot;timer-content&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">      &lt;p id=&quot;timer-content&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;script&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    // 设置计时器与起始时间</span><br><span class="line">    var timerElement = document.getElementById(&#x27;timer-content&#x27;);</span><br><span class="line">    var startDate = new Date(&lt;%= theme.timer.start_date %&gt;).getTime();</span><br><span class="line">    // 更新计时器显示的函数</span><br><span class="line">    function updateTimer() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      var now = new Date();</span><br><span class="line">      var timeDiff = now.getTime() - startDate;</span><br><span class="line">      // 转化输出格式</span><br><span class="line">      var days = Math.floor(timeDiff / (1000 * 60 * 60 * 24));</span><br><span class="line">      var showContent = &#x27;&lt;b&gt;&#x27; + days + &#x27;&lt;/b&gt; 天 &#x27;;</span><br><span class="line">      var hours = Math.floor((timeDiff % (1000 * 60 * 60 * 24)) / (1000 * 60 * 60));</span><br><span class="line">      var showContent = showContent + &#x27;&lt;b&gt;&#x27; + hours + &#x27;&lt;/b&gt; 时 &#x27;;</span><br><span class="line">      var minutes = Math.floor((timeDiff % (1000 * 60 * 60)) / (1000 * 60));</span><br><span class="line">      var showContent = showContent + &#x27;&lt;b&gt;&#x27; + minutes + &#x27;&lt;/b&gt; 分 &#x27;;</span><br><span class="line">      // var seconds = Math.floor((timeDiff % (1000 * 60)) / 1000);</span><br><span class="line">      // var showContent = showContent + &#x27;&lt;b&gt;&#x27; + seconds + &#x27;&lt;/b&gt; 秒 &#x27;;</span><br><span class="line">      </span><br><span class="line">      // 更新页面上的倒计时显示</span><br><span class="line">      timerElement.innerHTML = showContent;</span><br><span class="line">      setTimeout(updateTimer, 20000);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    // 初始调用</span><br><span class="line">    updateTimer();</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;/script&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;% &#125; %&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
