      <title>A Disadvantage of Apple Watch</title>
      <link href="/2023/10/16/Apple-Watch-Used/"/>
      <url>/2023/10/16/Apple-Watch-Used/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Generally speaking, I do love my Apple Watch. But what is to my disappointment is that it may cause burns on my wrist with it on while sleeping. I can clearly see the wound on my left wrist while taking a shower, because this is the only moment that I put my watch off.<br>But I still regard it as a common phenomenon when wearing a smart wearable device, because it seemed that I was also burned when I first wore my Mi Smart Band. This explanation may be more a tendentious defense than a seek of facts. But wish the incidental burn could disappear in the future.</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
