      <title>Countdown</title>
      <link href="/2023/09/17/Countdown/"/>
      <url>/2023/09/17/Countdown/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>鏖战一晚上，终于完成了首页的倒计时功能！感谢ChatGPT的倾情帮助～</p><p>以下是countdown.ejs的内容：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;% if (theme.countdown.on &amp;&amp; page.current === 1) &#123; %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;div class=&quot;countdown&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;h3 class=&quot;countdown-title&quot; style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;距离&lt;b style=&quot;color: #16a951;&quot;&gt;&lt;%= theme.countdown.title %&gt;&lt;/b&gt;还有&lt;/h3&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;div class=&quot;countdown-content&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">      &lt;p id=&#x27;countdown-content&#x27;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;script&gt;</span><br><span class="line">          // 设置截止时间</span><br><span class="line">          var targetDate = new Date(&lt;%= theme.countdown.end_date %&gt;).getTime();</span><br><span class="line">          // 设置是否精确到时/分/秒</span><br><span class="line">          var accuracyHour = false</span><br><span class="line">          var accuracyMinute = false</span><br><span class="line">          var accuracySecond = false</span><br><span class="line">          // 计算剩余时间</span><br><span class="line">          function updateCountdown() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            var now = new Date();</span><br><span class="line">            var timeLeft = targetDate - now.getTime();</span><br><span class="line">            // 计算剩余天、时、分、秒</span><br><span class="line">            var days = Math.floor(timeLeft / (1000 * 60 * 60 * 24));</span><br><span class="line">            var showContent = &#x27;&lt;b style=&quot;font-size: 25px; color: #107d3d;&quot;&gt;&#x27; + days + &#x27;&lt;/b&gt; 天 &#x27;;</span><br><span class="line">            if (accuracyHour) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">              var hours = Math.floor((timeLeft % (1000 * 60 * 60 * 24)) / (1000 * 60 * 60));</span><br><span class="line">              var showContent = showContent + &#x27;&lt;b&gt;&#x27; + hours + &#x27;&lt;/b&gt; 时 &#x27;;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125; else if (accuracyMinute) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">              var minutes = Math.floor((timeLeft % (1000 * 60 * 60)) / (1000 * 60));</span><br><span class="line">              var showContent = showContent + &#x27;&lt;b&gt;&#x27; + minutes + &#x27;&lt;/b&gt; 分 &#x27;;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125; else if (accuracySecond) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            var seconds = Math.floor((timeLeft % (1000 * 60)) / 1000);</span><br><span class="line">            var showContent = showContent + &#x27;&lt;b&gt;&#x27; + seconds + &#x27;&lt;/b&gt; 秒 &#x27;;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            // 更新页面上的倒计时显示</span><br><span class="line">            document.getElementById(&quot;countdown-content&quot;).innerHTML = showDay + showHour + showMin + showSec;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            if (timeLeft &gt; 0) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">              // 每秒钟更新一次倒计时</span><br><span class="line">              setTimeout(updateCountdown, 1000);</span><br><span class="line">            &#125; else &#123;</span><br><span class="line">              // 倒计时结束后显示消息</span><br><span class="line">              clearInterval(setTimeout(updateCountdown));</span><br><span class="line">              document.getElementById(&quot;countdown-content&quot;).innerHTML = &quot;0 天 0 时 0 分 0 秒&quot;;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">          &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">          // 初始调用</span><br><span class="line">          updateCountdown();</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;/script&gt;</span><br><span class="line">      &lt;/p&gt; </span><br><span class="line">    &lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;% &#125; %&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
