        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Made secondary menu for ‘Toolkits’ today. But I cannot understand how to add an icon for them. Even though the theme maker had offered several fa-icons in the original file, I still do not know if there are more icons like this or how can I find more.</p><p>Tried to add a photo as a icon, failed. Hope I can solve this tonight.</p><p>I also found that Aplipay QR code cannot show while WeixinPay QR code is working well. So how do all these bugs appear?</p><p>&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;<br>Added at 2023-09-14 03:08:40</p><p>Great! After searching for ages, I have understood how to add icons!</p><p>Thanks to the original author of the theme, who had added ‘fontawesome’ to CDN, everything I need to do is checking the name of the icon on <a href="https://fontawesome.com/icons">https://fontawesome.com/icons</a>! </p><p>My next goal is to fix the search fuction. Wish it could come true as soon as possible.</p><p>P.S. I still cannot tell the difference between hope and wish.</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
