        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="Why-do-I-write-my-thoughts-here"><a href="#Why-do-I-write-my-thoughts-here" class="headerlink" title="Why do I write my thoughts here?"></a>Why do I write my thoughts here?</h2><p>In fact, the establishment of this website is just an incident. But I think this is a perfect place to practise my English and say something privately. I believe only a few people are able to see it, let alone my acquaintants. So it is a safer place to express a feeling and might be more stable than Twitter, more free than WeChat, and more flexible than most domestic social media.</p><h2 id="My-goals"><a href="#My-goals" class="headerlink" title="My goals:"></a>My goals:</h2><ol><li>Wish I can fix bugs and keep it running. Though it can be visited from other devices in the afternoon, many new changes have made this website inaccessible from other devices, at least until the time I write down these words. I believe it will become better in the future.</li><li>Make my own theme. This theme (Bamboo) is downloaded on the Internet and is certainly used by many other people. Hope I can learn how to make a beautiful website and design my own page.</li><li>Split the Chinese and English section. Make different pages for different languages. Maybe the contents will differ from each other, too.</li></ol><p>Perhaps there are more goals. Maybe I am going to update it sometime.</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
